WEBVTT

00:06:29.249 --> 00:06:33.103
our opponent used
our own arguments against us.

00:06:33.103 --> 00:06:35.332
We ended up losing the popular vote.

00:06:35.332 --> 00:06:37.677
It was really terrible.

00:06:37.677 --> 00:06:43.836
The National Rifle Association --
yes, the American NRA --

00:06:43.836 --> 00:06:45.595
came to Brazil.

00:06:45.595 --> 00:06:48.695
They inundated our campaign
with their propaganda,

00:06:48.695 --> 00:06:50.238
that as you know,

00:06:50.238 --> 00:06:54.581
links the right to own guns
to ideas of freedom and democracy.

00:06:54.581 --> 00:06:58.458
They simply threw everything at us.

00:06:58.458 --> 00:07:00.385
They used our national flag,